{"tha-ap326:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap326:0.2":"Umapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap326:0.3":"Yannasamikattheraapadana ","tha-ap326:1.1":"“Jatiya sattavassoham, ","tha-ap326:1.2":"ahosim mantaparagu; ","tha-ap326:1.3":"Kulavattam adharesim, ","tha-ap326:1.4":"yanno ussahito maya. ","tha-ap326:2.1":"Cullasitisahassani, ","tha-ap326:2.2":"pasu hannanti me tada; ","tha-ap326:2.3":"Sarathambhupanitani, ","tha-ap326:2.4":"yannatthaya upatthita. ","tha-ap326:3.1":"Ukkamukhapahatthova, ","tha-ap326:3.2":"khadirangarasannibho; ","tha-ap326:3.3":"Udayantova suriyo, ","tha-ap326:3.4":"punnamayeva candima. ","tha-ap326:4.1":"Siddhattho sabbasiddhattho, ","tha-ap326:4.2":"tilokamahito hito; ","tha-ap326:4.3":"Upagantvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap326:4.4":"idam vacanamabravi. ","tha-ap326:5.1":"‘Ahimsa sabbapaninam, ","tha-ap326:5.2":"kumara mama ruccati; ","tha-ap326:5.3":"Theyya ca aticara ca, ","tha-ap326:5.4":"majjapana ca arati. ","tha-ap326:6.1":"Rati ca samacariyaya, ","tha-ap326:6.2":"bahusaccam katannuta; ","tha-ap326:6.3":"Ditthe dhamme parattha ca, ","tha-ap326:6.4":"dhamma ete pasamsiya. ","tha-ap326:7.1":"Ete dhamme bhavayitva, ","tha-ap326:7.2":"sabbasattahite rato; ","tha-ap326:7.3":"Buddhe cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap326:7.4":"bhavehi maggamuttamam’. ","tha-ap326:8.1":"Idam vatvana sabbannu, ","tha-ap326:8.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap326:8.3":"Mamevam anusasitva, ","tha-ap326:8.4":"vehasam uggato gato. ","tha-ap326:9.1":"Pubbe cittam visodhetva, ","tha-ap326:9.2":"paccha cittam pasadayim; ","tha-ap326:9.3":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap326:9.4":"tusitam upapajjaham. ","tha-ap326:10.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap326:10.2":"yada cittam pasadayim; ","tha-ap326:10.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap326:10.4":"buddhasannayidam phalam. ","tha-ap326:11.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap326:11.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap326:11.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap326:12.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma yannasamiko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap326:13.1":"Yannasamikattherassapadanam catuttham. "}